---
/**
 * NeoN ANTHEM Project Landing Page Component
 * 白背景のシンプルなランディングページ
 * 将来的にVOL.2以降や配信リンクを追加可能な構成
 */
---

<div class="anthem-page">
  <!-- Header with Back Button -->
  <header class="anthem-header">
    <a href="/" class="back-btn">
      <i class="fas fa-arrow-left"></i>
      <span>NeoN HOME</span>
    </a>
  </header>

  <!-- Hero Section -->
  <section class="anthem-hero">
    <img src="/images/anthem-logo.jpg" alt="NeoN ANTHEM PROJECT" class="anthem-logo" />
  </section>

  <!-- Concept Section -->
  <section class="anthem-concept">
    <p class="concept-lead">「NeoNに遊びに来ると曲ができる」</p>
    <div class="concept-text">
      <p>嘘じゃないです。<br>NeoNで生まれた収益でアーティストに楽曲制作を依頼します。</p>
      <p>とびっきりの<span class="highlight">"アンセム"</span>を注文しました。</p>
      <p>このアンセムはNeoN DJだけのものではありません。全国のROCK DJ、そして音楽を愛するすべてのリスナーのものです。</p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- VOL.1 Section -->
  <section class="anthem-volume" id="vol1">
    <h2 class="volume-title">第一弾</h2>
    <div class="volume-content">
      <img src="/images/anthem-vol1.jpg" alt="ANTHEM VOL.1" class="volume-image" />
      <div class="volume-artists">
        <h3 class="artists-label">参加アーティスト</h3>
        <ul class="artists-list">
          <li>空きっ腹に酒</li>
          <li>ビレッジマンズストア</li>
        </ul>
      </div>
      <!-- 配信リンク (リリース後に表示) -->
      <div class="streaming-links" id="vol1-streaming" style="display: none;">
        <h3 class="streaming-label">配信先</h3>
        <div class="streaming-buttons">
          <!-- リンクは後から追加 -->
          <a href="#" class="streaming-btn spotify">
            <i class="fab fa-spotify"></i>
            <span>Spotify</span>
          </a>
          <a href="#" class="streaming-btn apple">
            <i class="fab fa-apple"></i>
            <span>Apple Music</span>
          </a>
          <a href="#" class="streaming-btn youtube">
            <i class="fab fa-youtube"></i>
            <span>YouTube Music</span>
          </a>
        </div>
      </div>
      <!-- リリース前の表示 -->
      <div class="coming-soon-badge">
        <span>Coming Soon</span>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Future Volumes Placeholder -->
  <!--
  <section class="anthem-volume" id="vol2">
    <h2 class="volume-title">VOL.2</h2>
    <div class="volume-content">
      <img src="/images/anthem-vol2.jpg" alt="ANTHEM VOL.2" class="volume-image" />
      <div class="volume-artists">
        <h3 class="artists-label">参加アーティスト</h3>
        <ul class="artists-list">
          <li>アーティスト名</li>
        </ul>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
  -->

  <!-- Message Section -->
  <section class="anthem-message">
    <div class="message-content">
      <p>当プロジェクトは今後も継続していきます。</p>
      <p>ROCK DJシーン発のアンセムが生まれ続けます。第二弾、第三弾とみんなで紡いでいきましょう。</p>
      <p class="message-highlight">流行りは待つものではなく作るもの。<br>やってみよう。</p>
      <p class="message-signature">NeoN</p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Footer -->
  <footer class="anthem-footer">
    <a href="/" class="footer-home-btn">
      <i class="fas fa-home"></i>
      <span>NeoN HOME に戻る</span>
    </a>
    <p class="copyright">&copy; 2025 NeoN. All rights reserved.</p>
  </footer>
</div>

<style>
  /* ========================================
     Anthem Landing Page Styles
     白背景バージョン
     ======================================== */

  .anthem-page {
    background: #fff;
    color: #1a1a1a;
    min-height: 100vh;
    font-family: 'Helvetica Neue', Arial, sans-serif;
  }

  /* Header */
  .anthem-header {
    position: fixed;
    top: 0;
    left: 0;
    right: 0;
    padding: 1rem 1.5rem;
    background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.95);
    backdrop-filter: blur(10px);
    z-index: 100;
    border-bottom: 1px solid #eee;
  }

  .back-btn {
    display: inline-flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 0.5rem;
    color: #1a1a1a;
    text-decoration: none;
    font-size: 0.9rem;
    font-weight: 500;
    transition: color 0.3s ease;
  }

  .back-btn:hover {
    color: #fc00ff;
    text-shadow: none;
  }

  /* Hero */
  .anthem-hero {
    padding: 5rem 1.5rem 1rem;
    text-align: center;
    background: linear-gradient(180deg, #f8f8f8 0%, #fff 100%);
  }

  .anthem-logo {
    max-width: 400px;
    width: 80%;
    margin: 0 auto;
    border-radius: 8px;
  }

  /* Concept Section */
  .anthem-concept {
    padding: 1.5rem 1.5rem 3rem;
    max-width: 700px;
    margin: 0 auto;
    text-align: center;
  }

  .concept-lead {
    font-size: 1.5rem;
    font-weight: 700;
    margin-bottom: 2rem;
    color: #1a1a1a;
    letter-spacing: 0.05em;
  }

  .concept-text {
    font-size: 1rem;
    line-height: 2;
    color: #333;
  }

  .concept-text p {
    margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
  }

  .concept-text .highlight {
    color: #fc00ff;
    font-weight: 700;
  }

  /* Volume Section */
  .anthem-volume {
    padding: 3rem 1.5rem;
    background: #f8f8f8;
  }

  .volume-title {
    text-align: center;
    font-size: 2rem;
    font-weight: 700;
    letter-spacing: 0.3em;
    margin-bottom: 2rem;
    color: #1a1a1a;
  }

  .volume-content {
    max-width: 500px;
    margin: 0 auto;
    text-align: center;
  }

  .volume-image {
    width: 100%;
    border-radius: 12px;
    box-shadow: 0 10px 40px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
    margin-bottom: 2rem;
  }

  .artists-label,
  .streaming-label {
    font-size: 0.85rem;
    color: #888;
    letter-spacing: 0.2em;
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
    text-transform: uppercase;
  }

  .artists-list {
    list-style: none;
    padding: 0;
    margin: 0 0 2rem 0;
  }

  .artists-list li {
    font-size: 1.2rem;
    font-weight: 600;
    margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
    color: #1a1a1a;
  }

  /* Streaming Links */
  .streaming-links {
    margin-top: 2rem;
  }

  .streaming-buttons {
    display: flex;
    flex-wrap: wrap;
    justify-content: center;
    gap: 1rem;
  }

  .streaming-btn {
    display: inline-flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 0.5rem;
    padding: 0.75rem 1.5rem;
    border-radius: 30px;
    font-size: 0.9rem;
    font-weight: 600;
    text-decoration: none;
    transition: all 0.3s ease;
  }

  .streaming-btn.spotify {
    background: #1DB954;
    color: #fff;
  }

  .streaming-btn.apple {
    background: #FA233B;
    color: #fff;
  }

  .streaming-btn.youtube {
    background: #FF0000;
    color: #fff;
  }

  .streaming-btn:hover {
    transform: translateY(-2px);
    box-shadow: 0 5px 20px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.2);
    text-shadow: none;
  }

  /* Coming Soon Badge */
  .coming-soon-badge {
    display: inline-block;
    padding: 0.5rem 2rem;
    background: linear-gradient(135deg, #00fffc, #fc00ff);
    color: #fff;
    font-size: 0.9rem;
    font-weight: 700;
    letter-spacing: 0.2em;
    border-radius: 30px;
    margin-top: 1rem;
  }

  /* Message Section */
  .anthem-message {
    padding: 4rem 1.5rem;
    background: #fff;
  }

  .message-content {
    max-width: 600px;
    margin: 0 auto;
    text-align: center;
    font-size: 1rem;
    line-height: 2;
    color: #333;
  }

  .message-content p {
    margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
  }

  .message-highlight {
    font-size: 1.2rem;
    font-weight: 700;
    color: #1a1a1a;
    margin-top: 2rem;
  }

  .message-signature {
    font-size: 1.5rem;
    font-weight: 700;
    color: #1a1a1a;
    margin-top: 2rem;
    letter-spacing: 0.2em;
  }

  /* Footer */
  .anthem-footer {
    padding: 3rem 1.5rem;
    text-align: center;
    background: #1a1a1a;
    color: #fff;
  }

  .footer-home-btn {
    display: inline-flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 0.5rem;
    color: #888;
    text-decoration: none;
    font-size: 0.9rem;
    margin-bottom: 2rem;
    transition: color 0.3s ease;
  }

  .footer-home-btn:hover {
    color: #fff;
    text-shadow: none;
  }

  .copyright {
    font-size: 0.8rem;
    color: #666;
  }

  /* Responsive */
  @media (max-width: 600px) {
    .anthem-hero {
      padding: 5rem 1rem 2rem;
    }

    .anthem-logo {
      max-width: 300px;
    }

    .concept-lead {
      font-size: 1.2rem;
    }

    .volume-title {
      font-size: 1.5rem;
    }

    .artists-list li {
      font-size: 1rem;
    }

    .streaming-buttons {
      flex-direction: column;
      align-items: center;
    }

    .streaming-btn {
      width: 100%;
      max-width: 250px;
      justify-content: center;
    }
  }
</style>
